item.title: Impact | Quality above all
item.dc:creator: @g0d_of_war1 g0d of war1
item.description:
@g0d_of_war1 wrote:

Pretty good rsps if you ask me, haven’t played a good rsps in a while. The xp rate is pretty normal as in normal, a nice fair rate not too fast nor too slow. The economy is a nice growing economy I think the rsps has been up for about 1 month & a half and has a fair amount of players can buy things off players sell things someone is bound to buy it. There is a really nice feature when you load client you have a choice of a Hd graphics On or Off, choice of gamframe hitmarks, full screen or fixed but to me my fav is the hd graphics. One more cool feature is there is also quests to be completed, and the old evil bob event!

Read full topic
